
-rebuild gui with pyqt-webkit, so that the interface can be built using html/css/javascript/svg
-use pyinstaller to package the app. cross-platform and compatible with pyqt and opencv. https://github.com/pyinstaller/pyinstaller/wiki
-implement autotracing with potrace. http://potrace.sourceforge.net/ and https://github.com/flupke/pypotrace
-build ufo files out of the autotraced output. http://robofab.com/
-try tesseract OCR instead of OpenCV https://github.com/tesseract-ocr


